1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,200
To join the AI Literacy Class hands-on,

2
00:00:03,200 --> 00:00:06,500
you'll need a paid Claude account.

3
00:00:06,500 --> 00:00:09,800
Here's how — it takes about a minute.

4
00:00:10,200 --> 00:00:14,000
First, go to claude.ai

5
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:18,500
and sign in — or create a free account.

6
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:24,000
Then open the account menu

7
00:00:24,000 --> 00:00:28,500
(bottom-left, where your name is).

8
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:33,500
Click "Upgrade,"

9
00:00:33,500 --> 00:00:38,000
and choose the Pro plan.

10
00:00:39,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Enter your payment details and confirm.

11
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:49,500
You'll see "Pro" on your account once it's active.

12
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:55,500
That's it! Bring this account —

13
00:00:55,500 --> 00:01:00,000
logged in on your laptop — to class.

14
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:03,000
See you there!
